subsection.def:
current year (現年份), in
        relation to the compilation of a provisional register, means the year for which the
        provisional register is being compiled;

paragraph.content:
is eligible under section 5L of the Schedule to Cap. 569 to be registered as an ex-officio member
                    for the purpose of constituting the Election Committee to be constituted on 22
                    October 2021;

subsection.def:
body (團體) has the
                meaning given by section 2(1) of Cap.
                541B;

gale warning (烈風警告) has the
                same meaning as in the Judicial Proceedings (Adjournment During Gale Warnings)
                Ordinance (Cap. 62);

inclement weather warning day (惡劣天氣警告日) means a working day on which a gale
                warning or a rainstorm warning is in force at any time during the ordinary business
                hours of the Office;

paragraph.content:
a date is prescribed in this Regulation (whether by reference to a specific
                    day of a specific month or to a day otherwise ascertainable under this
                    Regulation) or is fixed under this Regulation;

a date is prescribed by reference to a specific day of a specific month in
                    a provision (former provision) specified in column 1 of Table
                    1;

a date is prescribed by reference to a specific day of a specific month in
                    a provision (former provision) specified in column 1 of Table
                    2;

the names of the persons in Chinese, arranged according to the number of
                    strokes of the Chinese characters of their respective surnames, are to be
                    recorded first;

